This is a hack command list:

Command		What it does

q(obj)		Quaff (drink) a potion.
Q		Quit the game.
w(obj)		Wield a weapon.
W(obj)		Wear armor.
e(obj)		Eat food.
r(obj)		Read a scroll.
R(obj)		Remove a ring you are wearing.
t(obj)		Throw an object.
T		Take off the armor you are wearing.
I(obj)		Print the object an inventory letter refers to.
i		List everything you are carrying.
o		Set options.
p(obj)		Zap (point) a wand.
P(obj)		Put on a ring.
s		Search for secret doors and traps (Only right next to you).
S		Save the game.
d(obj)		Drop something
(Hit <return> to continue)
f(dir)		Move in direction dir until you meet a door or side passage.
c(obj)		Call something.


To move in a direction, use the following list:

	y  k  u
	 \ | /
	h--@--l
	 / | \
	b  j  n

A capital letter will continue movement until you meet a door, a monster,
or a wall.
'f' followed by a letter will cotinue until you meet a side passage, or one
of the above.


